text: {"reviewer": "Alina P.", "product": "HydraCloud Daily Gel-Cream SPF 30", "rating": "5", "review": "Finally, a sunscreen that doesn’t sting! I expected chalky residue, but this gel sinks in clear—even over my Calm & Soothe Serum. No midday tightness, just bouncy skin and zero pilling under makeup.", "age": "35", "skin_type": "Dry/Sensitive Skin"}

{"reviewer": "Marcus J.", "product": "Clear Slate BHA Serum", "rating": "4", "review": "Week 2 and my blackheads are 70 % gone. Slight purging at first, but pairing it with Velvet Matte Pore Serum solved midday shine. Docked one star because the dropper dribbles.", "age": "27", "skin_type": "Oily/Acne-Prone"}

{"reviewer": "Priya S.", "product": "Flash Fade Spot Corrector", "rating": "3", "review": "Tiny dark spots on my cheeks faded noticeably after six weeks, but the citrus scent feels strong. Wish EverGlow would tone it down—or offer unscented.", "age": "30", "skin_type": "Hyperpigmentation Concern"}

{"reviewer": "Daniela K.", "product": "CalmCucumber pH Mist", "rating": "2", "review": "Wanted a gentle refresher, but the mister spits unevenly and left my cheeks tacky. Didn’t irritate my eczema, so two stars, but definitely needs packaging fix.", "age": "41", "skin_type": "Eczema-Prone"}

{"reviewer": "Hannah L.", "product": "ColorLock Vibrant-Hue Conditioner", "rating": "5", "review": "Been bleaching for years and this is the first silicone-free conditioner that detangles without dulling my copper. No heaviness, just mirror shine. Bonus: smells like fresh hibiscus!", "age": "29", "skin_type": "Color-Treated Hair"}

{"reviewer": "Ben T.", "product": "Sunrise Retinal Serum", "rating": "5", "review": "My first retinal—zero irritation. Texture is silky, and my forehead lines look softer after a month. Paired with BarrierFix Cream at night for extra comfort.", "age": "25", "skin_type": "Combination Skin"}

{"reviewer": "Lina M.", "product": "Deep Nourish Body Butter", "rating": "4", "review": "Thick but melts fast. Cleared the itchy patches on my legs in three days. Only wish the tub were bigger because I’m going through it quickly.", "age": "33", "skin_type": "Post-Partum Dryness"}

{"reviewer": "Oscar F.", "product": "Revive Citrus Shower Gel", "rating": "5", "review": "Love the zingy scent after a workout. Sulfate-free formula lathers surprisingly well and doesn’t strip—skin feels fresh, not squeaky.", "age": "29", "skin_type": "Gym Enthusiast"}

{"reviewer": "Claire H.", "product": "Velvet Night Repair Cream", "rating": "4", "review": "Rich but not greasy. Woke up glowier by week two and foundation glides on smoother. One star off for the heavy glass jar—beautiful but travel-unfriendly.", "age": "44", "skin_type": "Fine Lines & Dullness"}

{"reviewer": "Nina R.", "product": "FeatherLight Oil-Balance Conditioner", "rating": "4", "review": "Actually hydrates my ends without making roots limp. Scalp feels clean next day. Would love a bigger scent punch, but performance is A+.", "age": "31", "skin_type": "Oily Scalp / Dry Ends"}

{"reviewer": "Ethan G.", "product": "SunVeil Ultra-Light Fluid SPF 50", "rating": "2", "review": "Texture is amazing, but it stings my eyes when I sweat and leaves a slight shine on my darker skin tone. Works for casual days, not long runs.", "age": "38", "skin_type": "Outdoor Runner"}

{"reviewer": "Jada V.", "product": "GlowPrep 5 % Glycolic Toner", "rating": "5", "review": "Holy-grail for texture. Zero stinging, just glassy skin after two weeks. Love that it layers under the Clear Slate BHA on alternate nights.", "age": "22", "skin_type": "Acne-Prone"}

{"reviewer": "Ramon S.", "product": "ScalpBalance Anti-Dandruff Shampoo", "rating": "4", "review": "Flakes gone in three washes. Herbal scent is nice but strong; wife says it lingers. Still, scalp feels clean without tightness.", "age": "36", "skin_type": "Flaky Scalp"}

{"reviewer": "Keira D.", "product": "HydraDream Overnight Mask", "rating": "4", "review": "I slap this on after a 12-hour shift and wake up looking human. Only downside: the jar pumps out too much product if I’m not careful.", "age": "28", "skin_type": "Night-Shift Nurse"}

{"reviewer": "Oliver P.", "product": "AquaShield Barrier Booster", "rating": "4", "review": "Instant relief on angry cheeks. No fragrance burn, absorbs fast. Wish it came in a larger size for the price.", "age": "34", "skin_type": "Barrier-Compromised"}

{"reviewer": "Sasha L.", "product": "Arctic Hand Rescue Cream", "rating": "5", "review": "Thick, but sinks in before I finish a coffee. Cracks on my knuckles healed within days, and the oat scent is comforting.", "age": "41", "skin_type": "Frequent Hand-Washer"}

{"reviewer": "Gwen K.", "product": "SmoothLift Wrinkle Corrector", "rating": "3", "review": "Fine for daytime plumping, but pills under my silicone-free primer. Might keep it for night only.", "age": "50", "skin_type": "Mature Skin"}

{"reviewer": "Theo H.", "product": "SleekSilk Anti-Frizz Shampoo", "rating": "4", "review": "Not a miracle, but humidity halo is 70 % tamed. Works best with the matching conditioner. But bottle cap is hard to flip in the shower.", "age": "27", "skin_type": "Curly, Humid Climate"}

{"reviewer": "Melanie J.", "product": "Clarify Clay Rinse-Off Mask", "rating": "5", "review": "Ten-minute rescue for my nose + chin. Feels minty but not harsh. Pores visibly smaller the next morning.", "age": "30", "skin_type": "Congested T-Zone"}

{"reviewer": "Brent W.", "product": "Polish Glow Exfoliating Body Wash", "rating": "3", "review": "Scrubby beads feel great, but scent is lighter than expected and bottle runs out fast. Skin does feel smoother though.", "age": "24", "skin_type": "Gym-Goer"}

{"reviewer": "Norah F.", "product": "HydraCloud Daily Gel-Cream SPF 30", "rating": "4", "review": "Surprisingly hydrating in dry Arizona air. SPF is enough for office days. Loses a star because I still need heavier cream on cheekbones at night.", "age": "45", "skin_type": "Desert Climate"}
